(98, 4, 'bio', 'TUUR DEMEESTER\r\n<h2>MEET YOUR EXPERT</h2>\r\nTuur is a business cycle expert, Bitcoin veteran, and no stranger to volatile markets—before the age of 16 he had already traveled to three hyperinflationary economies. His subscription newsletter predicted the decline of the euro, and was the first to research Bitcoin in depth and recommend it as an investment. At the time, it seemed ludicrous. But within two years, his subscribers (and the world) watched as Bitcoin shot up in value by 23,000%!\r\n\r\nIn the Adamant Newsletter, you’ll receive exclusive analysis from Tuur. Analysis based on consulting with his global network of industry contacts, from attending select conferences, and his extensive market research.'),
