(178, 26, 'intro', '<h2>TRADITIONAL INVESTING IS BROKEN</h2>\r\nThe world''s economic climate is undergoing massive changes — a fact that traditional investment approaches fail to recognize.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Since 2007, global debt has ballooned from $43 trillion to $100 trillion.</li>\r\n	<li>Government debt in the West is at 110% of GDP, the highest ever.</li>\r\n	<li>Global interest rates are the lowest they have been in 1,000 years.</li>\r\n	<li>Plunging oil prices and a strong dollar are disrupting economies around the world.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This year a Chinese firm successfully 3D printed a five story apartment building.</li>\r\n	<li>This year, the first autonomous driving truck has been cleared for US roads.</li>\r\n	<li>The $5 billion Bitcoin industry is the world’s fastest area of startup investment.</li>\r\n	<li>In the last 4 years, the world gained a billion new internet users.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMost asset managers, even if they tell themselves otherwise, are trying to pick up pennies in front of a steamroller. The challenge for the intelligent investor today is to identify disruptive trends and macro distortions and to synthesize this information into a robust investment strategy. <strong>That''s where we come in.</strong>'),
(179, 26, '_intro', 'field_564842a78cb2b'),
(180, 26, 'newsletter_details', '<h2>The Adamant Newsletter</h2>\r\n<h6>Get Bigger Picture Insights.</h6>\r\nIn volatile times like these, it’s crucial to first carefully assess the macro-economic context before picking specific stocks, bonds, or currencies. Our research and experience will help you understand how to select the ideal markets first, and then move to specific investment opportunities within them.\r\n<h6>Understand Disruptive Opportunities</h6>\r\nDuring economic crises, old formulas stop working and new disruptive technologies create enormous investment opportunities. One such technology is Bitcoin and blockchain innovation. Having covered this market since 2011, we know how to filter out and deliver the information you need to make smart decisions.\r\n<h6>Access Original, Exclusive Research</h6>\r\nGetting ahead means having access to better resources. Join our newsletter to gain access to our exclusive network and read our original research.\r\n<h6>Get Ahead of Trends</h6>\r\nWith volatility on the rise in today’s markets, it’s vital to properly prepare for significant trends going forward. Receive predictions (backed up by research) on new trends and impending bull markets.\r\n<h2>Join the Adamant Newsletter and get instant access to expert advice</h2>\r\n<h2></h2>'),
(181, 26, '_newsletter_details', 'field_564844538cb2e'),
(182, 26, 'bio', 'Tuur Demeester\r\n<h2>Meet Your Expert</h2>\r\nTuur is a business cycle expert, Bitcoin veteran, and no stranger to volatile markets—before the age of 16 he had already traveled to three hyperinflationary economies. His subscription newsletter predicted the decline of the euro, and was the first to research Bitcoin in depth and recommend it as an investment. At the time, it seemed ludicrous. But within two years, his subscribers (and the world) watched as Bitcoin shot up in value by 23,000%!\r\n\r\nIn the Adamant Newsletter, you’ll receive exclusive analysis from Tuur. Analysis based on consulting with his global network of industry contacts, from attending select conferences, and his extensive market research.'),
